{"tid":1517753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"驚狗仔返學比人打！？其實仲有個方法","createTime":"2019-08-30T04:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T07:27:06.000Z","uid":13138,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3dcf0f4f1c26eb519fa007088821df042e46935a","tid":1517753,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hL7HPk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hL7HPk.jpg&h=71110608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搵個籠放啲狗仔入去，唔驚比同學仔之餘，一樣可以聽書！<br />\n<br />\n好似佢地老豆老母返工咁，行咇唔洗落車<br />\n老師幫狗仔推出推入，就唔驚比人打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都係個句，驚咪唔好返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd9b9232a57aba4b2f522e4646e44649c7fb49d","tid":1517753,"uid":266100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:24:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a505e99b107ecb6e061d58778a56564e3c7afe72","tid":1517753,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89df944f3b362c3c1c1397d5fb91eddbbc65f7f","tid":1517753,"uid":215861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:15:35.000Z","msg":"要多三個lone放手同頭呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c27f5a9df9c9d7f125399709db6289e5a897d8e","tid":1517753,"uid":2949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:22:34.000Z","msg":"整個牌印住警章寫明<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警員子女</span><br />\n真係離遠見到你都調頭走啦<br />\n邊個敢欺凌你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67ae28706c71b00634f979d5ab9b9507f7ffb96","tid":1517753,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c27f5a9df9c9d7f125399709db6289e5a897d8e","tid":1517753,"uid":2949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:22:34.000Z","msg":"整個牌印住警章寫明<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警員子女</span><br />\n真係離遠見到你都調頭走啦<br />\n邊個敢欺凌你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:10:14.000Z","msg":"狗仔"},{"pid":"8601d4b0081138c7044f2a76748ce1a77d18c54d","tid":1517753,"uid":2223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yhcNJOp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyhcNJOp.jpg&h=ba66b7d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1c52ce23b0a5a6607de03486852eaa334c23a58","tid":1517753,"uid":176657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:22:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f4329ff4e40fa22ad120972d60d38e7227150a","tid":1517753,"uid":247699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:22:49.000Z","msg":"體社署外抗議要求支援被捕社工<br />\n2019-08-30 HKT 10:52<br />\n <br />\n反送中社福聯合陣線早上到位於灣仔胡忠大廈的社署總部抗議，要求社署保障被捕社工、支援社工就反修例事件進行的人道救援、以及支援未成年被捕人士等。<br />\n<br />\n有社工說，至今有12名社工在衝突現場進行人道工作時以非法結集罪被捕，他認為警方做法荒謬，應該停止在有社福中心等地方施放催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n另外，組織表示，早前有年輕示威者在深水埗被捕後，警方拒絕讓社工提供支援及陪同前往警署，他們認為此舉嚴重剝奪對未成年被捕者的支援權利，絕不能夠接受。<br />\n<br />\n現場有數十人參與，又高叫口號，要求社署署長與在場人士公開對話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8osqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=e993c295\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&h=0c818935\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n由今朝到0830到而家,署長話見又話有誠意。結果餓到我地而家係胡忠8樓,社署點解唔肯見社工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你而家出黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0035804a51eda394daee1b1d6f7bcfc6f86ae91d","tid":1517753,"uid":145254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:23:11.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6def1c4a38e9f89dcb85fc2b0a5984ba33d812","tid":1517753,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8601d4b0081138c7044f2a76748ce1a77d18c54d","tid":1517753,"uid":2223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yhcNJOp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyhcNJOp.jpg&h=ba66b7d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:25:26.000Z","msg":"隔唔隔到催淚煙<br />\n一陣啲狗仔老豆射入學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374ba32f62f7e4224b7ab5b82037d3f8f700ab93","tid":1517753,"uid":119875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd6def1c4a38e9f89dcb85fc2b0a5984ba33d812","tid":1517753,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8601d4b0081138c7044f2a76748ce1a77d18c54d","tid":1517753,"uid":2223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yhcNJOp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyhcNJOp.jpg&h=ba66b7d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:25:26.000Z","msg":"隔唔隔到催淚煙<br />\n一陣啲狗仔老豆射入學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:27:06.000Z","msg":"你睇小AT力場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}